ly with given root\nnumber, we execute a further sieve to show that the root number is\nequidistributed and that the same average, now taken over only those curves of\ngiven root number, is also $3$. Finally, we apply the $p$-parity theorem of\nDokchitser--Dokchitser and a $p$-converse theorem of Burungale--Skinner to\nconclude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2022 17:14:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 08:10:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-07"}
