ormed nightly to forecast in\nadvance the PSF and support science operations of ground-based telescopes\nfacilities. The 'PSF forecast' option might therefore be added to ALTA Center\nor the operational forecast system that will be implemented soon at ESO.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2022 13:17:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-21"}
