ium a candid firm will switch to adopting a sparing strategy. The\nmodel illustrates how parameters such as time to mandatory disclosure, news\nintensity and pay-for-performance may drive such switching behaviour.\n$\\it{With\\,constant\\,pay\\,for\\,performance\\,parameters,\\,at\\,most\\,one\\,\nswitching\\,occurs.}$\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2022 14:46:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2023 13:08:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-03"}
